Description :
        A twitter comic spinoff by the author of Kuzumi-kun, Can't You Read the Room ? Revolving around the side characters of the previous series, Haruna, a scary looking man with a big heart and Ichikawa, an ice queen, and their relationship. Will the two kiss?
